# bolero fuzz: the exploration corpus is regenerated on every run (and cached in
# CI), so it is not tracked. Crash reproducers under __fuzz__/<target>/crashes/
# ARE tracked (see TESTING.md) so the blocking `test` job replays them forever.
**/__fuzz__/**/corpus/

.zed
.idea
